://www.macrumors.com/2025/01/16/ios-18-3-news-news-notifications-remavy/”>;来自&lt;em>; macrumors &lt;/em>; &lt;/a>;和&lt;a href =“ https://9to5mac.com/2025/01/16/ios-18-3-t-temporame-disables-disables-disables-papple-intelligence-intelligence-notification-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries-summaries- for-select-apps-more/“>; &lt;em>; 9to5mac &lt;/em>; &lt;/a>;。 Apple Intelligence驱动的功能不准确地总结了媒体的内容&lt;a href =“ https://www.theverge.com/2025/2025/1/6/24337681/apple-inple--inple-inple--inple-inple--inple--inpelligence-summ--------news-news-news-news-luigi--luig-igi------news-luigi---------news-luigi-i-- mangione-response“>;例如BBC &lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =“ 5vebzm”>;苹果将通过“未来软件更新”来重新启用通知随着它继续在该功能上工作，&lt;em>; 9to5mac &lt;/em>;报告。在新的Beta中，Apple将清楚地表明，通知摘要功能是Beta，并且“可能包含错误”。让您从iOS 18.3中的锁定屏幕或通知中心中禁用特定应用程序的通知，通过“刷卡，点击&#39;选项&#39;，然后选择“关闭摘要”。锁定屏幕可以更轻松地分开通知摘要和标准通知。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class =“ c-float-Left c-float-hang”>; &lt;旁边id =“ jhlpwj”>; &lt;div div data-anthem-component =“ readmore” data-anthem-component-data =&#39;{{ “故事”：[{{“ title”：“苹果AI通知摘要存在；很少有用，通常有趣的“”，“ url”：“ https：//www.theverge.com/2024/11/11/12/24289939/apple-inpelligence-intelligence-intelligence-ai-notification-summaries-summaries-awkward-funny-bad”}}&#39;>; &lt;/div >; &lt;/fased>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id =“ z6oovi”>; &lt;em>; verge &lt;/em>;与Apple联系，要求提供有关这些更改的更多信息，但没有立即听回来。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =“ 3HQOA1”>;上个月，&lt;a href =“ https://www.theverge.com/2024/2024/13/13/24320689/apple-inpleligence-inpelligence-summargence-summary-bbc-news -UnitedHealthCare-Luigi-Mangione“>; BBC召集了Apple &lt;/a>;在公司的通知摘要功能错误地汇总了其对UnitedHealth射击者的报道，这表明该媒体报道Luigi Mangione开枪打死了自己。 &lt;a href =“ https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/6/24337681/apple-inpelligence-summary-bbc-news-news-news-news-news-news-news-mangione-response-”出门更新，以“进一步澄清显示的文本是由Apple Intelligence提供的摘要。” &lt;/p>; &lt;p ID =“ bk4auu”>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/16/24345331/apple-notification-summaries-pause-news-ios-18-3-beta" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/16/24345331/apple-notification-summaries-pause-pause-news-ios-18-3-beta</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2025-01-16T14：34：41-05：00</published><updated> 2025-01-16T14：34：41-05：00</updated><title>以下是目前最优惠的 Apple Watch 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figug>; &lt;img alt =“一个人做双尾手势来决定文本的人。” src =“ https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nhr9atm7gwfscjtvyakoqemuqa=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vo x-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66976955/236790_apple_watch_9_9_ultra_2_akrales_0710.70.jpg“ />; &lt;figcaption>; &lt;em>;最后一代系列9与系列10没有什么不同，起价为279美元。&lt; /em>; |照片由Amelia Holowaty Krales/The Verge &lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/fig>; &lt;p id =“ 5yaz1u”>; 9月，苹果推出了最新的智能手表，介绍了&lt;a href =“ https://wwww.theverge.com/ 24246464/Apple-Watch-series-10-Review-SmartWatch-Wearables”>; Apple Watch系列10 &lt;/a>;与A &lt;a &lt;a href =“ https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/19/24248380/apple-watch-ultra-2-black-smartwatch-wearables”>; black Rendition>; black Rendition &lt;/a>; ：//www.theverge.com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-review-double-tap-precision-finding-siri>; Apple Watch ultra 2 &lt;/a>;。每个可穿戴设备都有自己的利弊，&lt;a href =“ https://www.theverge.com/23369207/apple-watch-se-se-se-2022-review-smartwatch”>;第二基因Apple Watch SE &lt;/ a>;，但是最近引入新的可穿戴设备也意味着现在市场上的Apple Watch模型比以往任何时候都多，还有更多的交易。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class =“ C-Float-Left c-float-hang“>; &lt;div id =“ cwuc7k”>; &lt;div div data-anthem-component =“旁边：11906226”>; &lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id =“ shcaqk”>;但是有了所有这些选择，您应该选择哪一个？一般而言，您想购买可以负担得起的最新手表，以便它继续从Apple接收软件更新。最新更新，&lt;a href =“ https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/25/24253366/watch-os-11-11-apple-watch-smartwatch”>; Watchos 11 &lt;/a>;在Apple Watch Series 6和更新的情况下，最终留下了仍然使用较旧的系列4或系列5的人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =“ c0aqbe”>;是说，从最新的手表那里拿起手表（或最近的）一代可确保您获得带有更新设计的智能手表，功能强大和大量传感器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =“ m0l8kw”>;现在，让我们开